snippet.title: Blood gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Blood, Dos PC game produced by Monolith in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/blood/119/
You will re-live in a very gore atmosphere. First stage passed and second stage introduction.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
The Typing of the Dead - https://youtu.be/Zs3M6oDcPlU
